title: Fruity Paralysis
ingredients: ['1 cupful ice', '1 1/2 tablespoons vodka', '2 teaspoons amaretto liqueur', '1 1/2 tablespoons peach schnapps', '1 1/2 tablespoons coconut flavoured rum', '2 teaspoons melon liqueur', '3 tablespoons orange juice', '1 1/2 tablespoons pineapple juice', '85ml cranberry juice', '1 twist lemon zest']
